{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/ansi-sql-condition-statement/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"김동호 블로그"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"696d340c-bc17-50cf-84c5-e6e2e311a8fb","excerpt":"1. CASE 문 표준 SQL은  문을 사용한다.  문은 두 가지 방식으로 사용될 수 있다. 1.1. 검색형 CASE 1.2. 단순형 CASE 2. NULL 관련 특정 값이 NULL인 경우에 처리하기 위한 표준 함수인 가 있다. 2.1. COALESCE…","html":"<h1 id=\"1-case-문\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-case-%EB%AC%B8\" aria-label=\"1 case 문 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. CASE 문</h1>\n<p>표준 SQL은 <code class=\"language-text\">CASE</code> 문을 사용한다.<br>\n<code class=\"language-text\">CASE</code> 문은 두 가지 방식으로 사용될 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"11-검색형-case\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11-%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89%ED%98%95-case\" aria-label=\"11 검색형 case permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.1. 검색형 CASE</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CASE</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> score <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">90</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">THEN</span> <span class=\"token string\">'A'</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> score <span class=\"token operator\">>=</span> <span class=\"token number\">80</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">THEN</span> <span class=\"token string\">'B'</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">ELSE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'C'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">END</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"12-단순형-case\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#12-%EB%8B%A8%EC%88%9C%ED%98%95-case\" aria-label=\"12 단순형 case permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1.2. 단순형 CASE</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">CASE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">year</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">THEN</span> <span class=\"token string\">'신입'</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">WHEN</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">THEN</span> <span class=\"token string\">'주니어'</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">ELSE</span> <span class=\"token string\">'경력'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">END</span></code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"2-null-관련\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-null-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8\" aria-label=\"2 null 관련 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. NULL 관련</h1>\n<p>특정 값이 NULL인 경우에 처리하기 위한 표준 함수인 <code class=\"language-text\">COALESCE()</code>가 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"21-coalesce\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#21-coalesce\" aria-label=\"21 coalesce permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.1. COALESCE</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">COALESCE()</code>에는 무한대의 인자를 넣을 수 있고, 나열된 인자 중 NULL이 아닌 첫 번째 값을 반환한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">COALESCE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>col1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> col2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"22-nullif\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#22-nullif\" aria-label=\"22 nullif permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.65 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2.2. NULLIF</h2>\n<p>두 값이 같으면 NULL을, 다르면 첫 번째 값을 반환한다.<br>\n주로 0으로 나누기 에러를 방지하거나, 의미 없는 특정 데이터(예: 공백)을 NULL로 처리할 때 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token keyword\">SELECT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">NULLIF</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>col1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> col2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#1-case-%EB%AC%B8\">1. CASE 문</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#11-%EA%B2%80%EC%83%89%ED%98%95-case\">1.1. 검색형 CASE</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#12-%EB%8B%A8%EC%88%9C%ED%98%95-case\">1.2. 단순형 CASE</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#2-null-%EA%B4%80%EB%A0%A8\">2. NULL 관련</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#21-coalesce\">2.1. COALESCE</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#22-nullif\">2.2. NULLIF</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[SQL] ANSI 표준 SQL의 조건식","date":"2026년 2월 28일","dateISO":"2026-02-28","description":"ANSI SQL의 조건식에 대해 기록한 글입니다.","tags":["SQL"]}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/sql-union-and-union-all/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[SQL] UNION과 UNION ALL 정리"}},"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"696d340c-bc17-50cf-84c5-e6e2e311a8fb","previousPostId":"79822319-2e0e-56f2-b737-4f8582103960","nextPostId":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2637872971","3361002528","3414707483"],"slicesMap":{}}